metadata.name: Hex AI
metadata.description:
Hex is the first Blockchain Certificate of Deposit.

Hex was launched as a complete product, immutable without any admin access or backdoors.

The goal of Hex was to remove all counterparty risks from compound investments.

Created by Richard Heart
